OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1963FThe first edition of The Dick
OL,7,FEmery Show airs on BBC TV.
OL,8,
OL,9,CG1965FThe final episode of Monitor
OL,10,Fairs on BBC One.
OL,11,
OL,12,CG1973FThe first episode of Jack the
OL,13,FRipper airs on BBC One. Radio Times: "A
OL,14,Fdocumentary investigation, in six
OL,15,Fepisodes, into the facts of the
OL,16,FWhitechapel Murders of 1888 -conducted
OL,17,Fby TV's two best-known investigators,
OL,18,FDet-Chief Supt Barlow and Det-Chief
OL,19,FSupt Watt. With Stratford Johns as
OL,20,FBarlow and Frank Windsor as Watt."
